channel.description:
[B][COLOR=Teal]Runescape 317 - 667[/COLOR][/B] [COLOR=DarkOrange] Why starting this project again? Because i got 50+ pm's of release this again, but since the mod has locked my thread and they're saying it isn't mine i'm starting with a fresh new client BUT with help of kenneh and Flamable i'm able to make a client with all 667+ data. Im using the server that Hayzie released and i'm just simply adding everything i like to add and a few tutorials/snippet from the tutorial/snippets section!
Remember: I'm not a perfectionist! i try to make it as good as i can but i cannot make it perfect so dont flame me that sometimes some skills etc are not 100% like the real Runescape
Btw for all you guys out there, you'll be happy because this time it does not have an anti-leech![/color]
[COLOR=teal][U]Download link server:[/U][/COLOR] [url=http://uppit.com/0qqxqwkqnm9s/Runescape_317_-_667_server_by_AFG.zip]Download Runescape.317.667.server.AFG.zip @ UppIT[/url]
[COLOR=teal][U]Download link client:[/U][/COLOR] http://www.multiupload.nl/VGHOBML75R mirror: http://up.ht/KVpqcV
[B][COLOR=DarkOrange]NOTE: This is just for a base, not everything is 100% done![/COLOR][/B]
[COLOR=Teal][B]Update log client & server:[/B][/COLOR] [code]Starting again: All standart thing from the normal PI. Added Firemaking Improved runecrafting 717 underlay flo.dat 717 overlay flo.dat 667 animations 667 gfx's Thanks to kenneh and flamable i added 667 maps. Made Edge as Home New training areas New smithing and mining places Thieving is ATM only for npc's added new Background Slayer base is added, just need to improve it more New loginbox & buttons. added new logo added serverside skillmenu updated to 459 gameframe. Oldschool 317 prayers All fish etc are cookable new cooking&fishing place Improved woodcutting( not the good animation) Xp remaining in skills tab started on agility, need to have 667 obj. id's to finish. fixed grey shiny roofs! full fights pits added, no bugs. clipped firemaking Highscores added IG for the best 50 ranks. added correct animation and gfx for teleport Wildy ditch is now working.[/code]
